            <scopecontent id="aspace_d55464ef9d092e7d313013097f691f2a">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Series I consists chiefly of letters from Leonard H. Swett to his mother and father in the 1870s and 1880s, including letters from the American West, where he worked with the United States Geological Survey. The series also includes other family correspondence and the records of geneaology research apparently carried out by Swett's daughter Laura Rose Swett (born 1897).</p>
            </scopecontent>
